 day that the LORD spake with Moses in mount Sinai.","year":-1490},{"id":"recKeuth44Em6snhm","ref":"Num.3.2","text":"And these are the names of the sons of Aaron; Nadab the firstborn, and Abihu, Eleazar, and Ithamar.","year":-1490},{"id":"recoLdkXTxdSwzWD5","ref":"Num.3.3","text":"These are the names of the sons of Aaron, the priests which were anointed, whom he consecrated to minister in the priest’s office.","year":-1490},{"id":"recBdnANWMmiQrU9u","ref":"Num.3.4","text":"And Nadab and Abihu died before the LORD, when they offered strange fire before the LORD, in the wilderness of Sinai, and they had no children: and Eleazar and Ithamar ministered in the priest’s office in the sight of Aaron their father.","year":-1490},{"id":"recz0TweGKS2fqstP","ref":"Num.3.5","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,","year":-1490},{"id":"recq56fIj0qPWW8Fj","ref":"Num.3.6","text":"Bring the tribe of Levi near, and present them before Aaron the priest, that they may minister unto him.","year":-1490},{"id":"recXrKRQ3kGphgiqc","ref":"Num.3.7","text":"And they shall keep his charge, and the charge of the whole congregation before the tabernacle of the congregation, to do the service of the tabernacle.","year":-1490},{"id":"recIhYcUGLsnV1vB3","ref":"Num.3.8","text":"And they shall keep all the instruments of the tabernacle of the congregation, and the charge of the children of Israel, to do the service of the tabernacle.","year":-1490}]}
